WEBVTT

00:01.059 --> 00:03.195
- Previously on The Originals...
- Maxine.

00:03.198 --> 00:04.755
It's Adam... he never came home.

00:04.757 --> 00:06.357
I've looked everywhere.

00:06.359 --> 00:07.391
Hope?

00:07.393 --> 00:09.226
- I had a bad dream.
- It's all right.

00:09.228 --> 00:10.228
You're safe.

00:11.297 --> 00:13.430
Why are you doing this to me?

00:13.432 --> 00:15.419
Your grandma's
maiden name was Malraux.

00:15.422 --> 00:17.295
You're the last of your pack,
that makes you special.

00:17.297 --> 00:18.836
You got my venom. When do I get to go?

00:18.838 --> 00:20.871
I barely had enough
to make the antivenom.

00:20.873 --> 00:23.941
If any of my family are ever
bitten again, we'll need more.

00:25.678 --> 00:27.911
Marcel, yeah, this city is in danger.

00:27.913 --> 00:29.413
And it might just be all my fault.

00:29.415 --> 00:32.235
I can sense Klaus is
still in New Orleans.

00:32.238 --> 00:33.676
We free Niklaus today.

00:33.679 --> 00:36.120
This spell is strong. I'll
need someone to channel.

00:36.122 --> 00:38.255
Whatever happens, don't
stop until Niklaus is free.

00:38.257 --> 00:40.424
Nik!

00:40.426 --> 00:42.192
You're ready to see your little girl?

00:42.194 --> 00:43.901
- Want me to wake her for you?
- No.

00:43.904 --> 00:46.070
Let's let her sleep.

00:48.534 --> 00:50.634
What's the holdup?

00:50.636 --> 00:52.569
All right, we rescued Nik,
we escaped mortal danger...

00:52.571 --> 00:56.073
Why are we not on a
private jet to Saint-Tropez?

00:56.075 --> 00:58.275
You can catch up on the last five years

00:58.277 --> 01:00.110
when we're on our way... I assure you

01:00.112 --> 01:01.378
you haven't missed much.

01:01.380 --> 01:02.713
Circumstances have changed.

01:02.715 --> 01:04.515
We will leave here soon enough.

01:04.516 --> 01:05.883
We have our niece to consider.

01:05.885 --> 01:07.184
Kol has a point.

01:07.186 --> 01:09.687
We need to put an ocean between us

01:09.689 --> 01:11.522
and Marcel Gerard as soon as possible.

01:11.524 --> 01:12.890
We're not going anywhere today.

01:12.892 --> 01:14.725
I want one day of peace with my daughter

01:14.727 --> 01:15.859
before we uproot her.

01:15.861 --> 01:18.929
- Any delay is a risk.
- One day.

01:18.931 --> 01:21.131
We're in the middle of
nowhere, the house is cloaked,

01:21.133 --> 01:22.800
we weren't followed, and I'm not asking!

01:27.665 --> 01:30.494
Everybody, look who's awake.

01:38.751 --> 01:40.417
Hello.

01:42.021 --> 01:44.254
Hello.

01:45.391 --> 01:48.025
Mom, can I go play in the garden?

01:48.027 --> 01:49.193
Yeah.

01:49.195 --> 01:51.295
Sure.

